  "title": "Regional Technical Sales Manager(Linear Motion Crane Solutions)",
  "description": "<p><strong>about the company</strong></p><p>Our client is a leading precision engineering company.They Committed to deliver strong service and forge meaningful partnerships in their industry.</p><p><strong>about the job</strong></p><ul><li>Responsible for Sales Targets and Annual Forecast / Budget for the SEA region</li><li>Establishing new, and maintaining existing, relationships with customers</li><li>Managing and interpreting customer requirements</li><li>Develop and monitor the market in the assigned area</li><li>Generate leads and identify opportunities.</li><li>Provide technical sales presentations, technical support, customer training, applications guidance</li><li>Prepare technical proposal and commercial proposal</li><li>Generate credible and up to date sales prediction</li><li>Ensure business objectives are met within the timeline</li><li>Assist in providing sales forecast and market reports</li><li>Manage the customer database</li></ul><p><strong>job requirement</strong></p><ul><li>Degree/Diploma in Mechanical / Electrical Engineering or related discipline</li><li>Min 8 years sales of experience in linear motion machinery environment</li><li>Able to travel to overseas for work assignment (about 60% S.E.A)</li></ul><p>If you are interested in the position, kindly apply to this job or send your CVs to yitwei.kwan(@)randstad.com.sg<br />We regret that only shortlisted candidates will be contacted<br />EA: 94C3609 / R1325913</p>",
